data.description: **Seller is offering a $5,000 CREDIT for buyer to use as closing costs or buy down the interest rate - whichever is best for buyer's needs.** Welcome to this beautiful well maintained ranch style home located in the South Point District of Pueblo. Home of the Colorado State Fair and Chili Festival. This home includes 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The kitchen area is spacious and open with stainless steel appliances. Family and dining room give this home a cozy feel with fresh carpet throughout. Plus a private laundry room area that can hold full size washer and dryer. Exit out into the private fenced backyard with a stunning enclosed Sunroom. Landscaped yard with plenty of shade from the covered back patio. The attached workshop brings additional square footage to the home. This home has extra space for recreational vehicles, work and business vehicles, etc. Driveways from front to back! Large driveway area with gated entrance. This is a must see to take in the amount of additional space. Schedule your showing TODAY! Showings begin Thursday 9/21.
